{% comment %}
  sections/homepage-hero.liquid
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Jedi homepage hero section.

  Rendered after the path-chooser entry screen fades out.
  Only styled when body[data-gf-side="light"] is present — set by path-chooser.js
  after the visitor chooses Light Side.

  Structure:
    <section>               ← full-bleed, Coruscant night image as background
      <div> overlay         ← dark gradient + Force glow layered over the image
        <div> gf-inner      ← 80% width content box, left-aligned text
          <p>  eyebrow      ← "Light Side Artifacts" with left-side decorative line
          <h1> title        ← main headline, "Legend." in Force blue
          <p>  sub          ← supporting sentence, Inter, muted white
          <a>  button       ← filled blue CTA, hover flips to outline style
      <p> location          ← "Planet / CORUSCANT" credit, bottom-right corner
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} Load this section's stylesheet {% endcomment %}
{{ 'homepage-hero.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="gf-hero full-width" aria-label="Hero">

  {% comment %}
    Overlay div — sits on top of the background image.
    Holds the dark gradient and Force glow so they layer cleanly
    without interfering with the image itself.
  {% endcomment %}
  <div class="gf-hero__overlay">

    {% comment %}
      gf-inner — the shared content width class (80%, max 1100px).
      Left-aligns all the text content within the full-bleed section.
    {% endcomment %}
    <div class="gf-inner">

      {% comment %}
        Eyebrow — left-aligned label above the headline.
        Line appears only on the left side (::before only).
      {% endcomment %}
      <p class="gf-hero__eyebrow">Light Side Artifacts</p>

      {% comment %}
        Headline — white with the word "Legend." highlighted in Force blue.
        The <span> lets us target just that word with a different color.
      {% endcomment %}
      <h1 class="gf-hero__title">Forge Your <span class="gf-hero__accent">Legend.</span></h1>

      {% comment %}
        Subtext — one supporting sentence in Inter, muted white.
      {% endcomment %}
      <p class="gf-hero__sub">
        The galaxy's finest relics, forged for those who stand for peace and the Force.
      </p>

      {% comment %}
        CTA Button — links to the Light Side collection.
        Filled blue at rest, flips to transparent outline on hover.
      {% endcomment %}
      <a href="{{ routes.collections_url }}/light-side" class="gf-hero__btn">
        Shop the Collection
      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

  {% comment %}
    Location credit — sits in the bottom-right corner of the section.
    "Planet / CORUSCANT" styled like a film location card.
  {% endcomment %}
  <p class="gf-hero__location">
    <span class="gf-hero__location-label">Planet</span>
    <span class="gf-hero__location-divider">/</span>
    <span class="gf-hero__location-name">Coruscant</span>
  </p>

</section>
